            <history-note id="DLM81216"><amended-provision>Section 58(1)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM331111">section 200</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Crown Entities Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 115).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM81217"><amended-provision>Section 58(1)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 May 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM348477">section 5(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>New Zealand Public Health and Disability Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 63).</history-note>
